# OpenMultiTrack

Read `docs/AGENTS.md` before non-trivial changes. Status tracker: `docs/PROJECT_STATUS.md`.

## Constraints (non-negotiable)
- No Google Play Services, Firebase, GMS, ads, or telemetry
- FOSS dependencies only; GPLv3-or-later
- Real-time audio in C++/Oboe (`audio-engine`); no blocking on audio thread
- Debug APK only in CI; same artifact for F-Droid repo and GitHub Releases
- Use committed `keystore/debug.keystore` for signing

## Conventions
- Conventional commits (`feat:`, `fix:`, `BREAKING CHANGE`)
- Push to `main`; no co-author trailers
- Update `docs/PROJECT_STATUS.md` when milestone status changes
- Validate hardware assumptions in `docs/hardware-assumptions.md` — many are UNVERIFIED

## Next milestone
M3: playback seek + transport UI + sample-aligned engine seek (see PROJECT_STATUS.md)
